# RentSphere

## Project Purpose

RentSphere is a modern house rental platform that connects property owners and tenants in a secure and user-friendly environment. Owners can list rental properties, tenants can browse and book properties, and administrators can manage platform activities efficiently.

### Authentication & Authorization

- Secure authentication using Better Auth
- Role-based access control (Admin, Owner, Tenant)
- Protected routes and APIs using JWT verification

### Property Management

- Owners can add new rental properties
- Owners can update property information
- Owners can delete their properties
- Property approval and rejection system

### Tenant Features

- Browse all available properties
- Search and filter properties
- Add properties to favorites
- Book rental properties online
- View booking history

### Admin Features

- Manage users and roles
- Approve or reject property listings
- Provide rejection feedback to owners
- Monitor platform activities

### Payment System

- Secure online payments using Stripe
- Booking confirmation after successful payment
- Transaction tracking

### Reviews & Feedback

- Tenants can submit property reviews
- Rating system for properties
- Admin rejection feedback system

### Responsive Design

- Mobile-friendly UI
- Tablet and desktop support
- Modern dashboard experience

